WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.700
All right, I have what I need.

2
00:00:02.700 --> 00:00:08.100
I am installing the local CTO stack now: first the container runtime checks, then kind, kubectl, Helm, and Argo CD if anything is missing.

3
00:00:08.100 --> 00:00:14.200
After that I bring up the Kind Kubernetes cluster, add ingress, metrics-server for Lens, and the Argo CD CRDs and controllers.

4
00:00:14.200 --> 00:00:21.446
Then I write the local secrets, register the CTO controller plus the Morgan bot and supporting platform apps, and let the CRDs take inventory so the install can reconcile the rest from GitOps.
